<section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock '   itemprop="text" ><h2 style="text-align: center;">An exclusive marketplace<strong>like no other</strong></h2>
</div></section>
<div  class='hr hr-short hr-center  avia-builder-el-11  el_after_av_textblock  el_before_av_textblock '><span class='hr-inner ' ><span class='hr-inner-style'></span></span></div>
<section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock '   itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: center;">We don't just assign freelancers to your project, we take a hands on approach by managing our talent to ensure your expectations are clearly communicated and projects are completed on time</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><div class='avia-double-buttons '><a href='http://hooros.co.za/home/register'  class='avia-double-button avia-double-button-1'>Client Sign Up</a><span class='button_or'>or</span><a href='http://hooros.co.za/home/login'  class='avia-double-button avia-double-button-2'>Client Login</a></div></p>
</div></section>
