n='true' data-av_icon='4' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello''></div><div data-priciple-logo-text='4' class='avia-priciple-logo-text avia-priciple-logo-text-4'><div class='avia-priciple-logo-text-inner'><strong>Cost Effective outsourcing</strong><span>Hooros is a cost effective outsourcing solution</span></div></div><div data-priciple-logo='5' class='avia-priciple-logo avia-priciple-logo-5 iconfont aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='5' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello''></div><div data-priciple-logo-text='5' class='avia-priciple-logo-text avia-priciple-logo-text-5'><div class='avia-priciple-logo-text-inner'><strong>Simplicity</strong><span>Hooros offers a simple service that cuts out the many layers you would have to go through to employ talent, particularly talent from outside of the country. You never have to worry about employment agents, visa applications and onerous labour law requirements again</span></div></div><div data-priciple-logo='6' class='avia-priciple-logo avia-priciple-logo-6 iconfont aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='6' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello''></div><div data-priciple-logo-text='6' class='avia-priciple-logo-text avia-priciple-logo-text-6'><div class='avia-priciple-logo-text-inner'><strong>Accountability</strong><span>Hooros gives you peace of mind by managing all freelancers on our platform to ensure they deliver on your needs on time and in accordance to the standards you set</span></div></div></div></div>
